Azure VM Start/Stop PowerShell Script
Pehle aapko Azure PowerShell module install aur login karna hoga:

Install-Module -Name Az -AllowClobber -Scope CurrentUser
Import-Module Az
Connect-AzAccount


# VM ka naam yahan likhiye
$vmName = "MyVMName"

# VM ko start karne ke liye
Start-VM -Name $vmName

# VM ko stop karne ke liye (graceful shutdown)
Stop-VM -Name $vmName -Force

# Azure resource group aur VM naam
$resourceGroup = "MyResourceGroup"
$vmName = "MyVM"
Phir VM start/stop ke liye:

# VM start karne ke liye
Start-AzVM -ResourceGroupName $resourceGroup -Name $vmName

# VM stop karne ke liye
Stop-AzVM -ResourceGroupName $resourceGroup -Name $vmName -Force
